OL,3,CRebecca Ferguson 'tried reaching out'
OL,4,Cto X Factor co-star Liam Payne
OL,6,FRebecca Ferguson said she had
OL,7,Fattempted to contact her former X
OL,8,FFactor co-star Liam Payne a week
OL,9,Fbefore his death because she had been
OL,10,F"worried about him for a while".
OL,12,FThe singer-songwriter, who is from
OL,13,FLiverpool, and appeared in the final
OL,14,Fof The X Factor with One Direction in
OL,15,F2010, said she was "in denial, shocked
OL,16,Fand hurt" after Payne fell to his
OL,17,Fdeath from a hotel balcony in Buenos
OL,18,FAires, Argentina.
