OL,3,CRebecca Ferguson 'tried reaching out'
OL,4,Cto X Factor co-star Liam Payne
OL,6,FFerguson said she had attempted to
OL,7,Fcontact Payne "last Saturday" as she
OL,8,Fsaid she could see he was struggling.
OL,10,F"I sent a message to some of the fans
OL,11,Fand I said: 'I'm really worried about
OL,12,FLiam, how do I get in touch with him?'
OL,13,Fand no-one knew how," the 38-year-old
OL,14,Fsaid on a live X Space with One
OL,15,FDirection fans.
