OL,3,CRebecca Ferguson 'tried reaching out'
OL,4,Cto X Factor co-star Liam Payne
OL,6,F"But I've been worried about him for a
OL,7,Fwhile because I could see that he was
OL,8,Fnot in a good place, and I thought he
OL,9,Fmight have been triggered by a lot of
OL,10,Fthe stuff that has been in the news
OL,11,Fhere lately as well."
OL,13,FFerguson said she joined the live X
OL,14,Fchat, titled Liam and Directioners,
OL,15,Fbecause "I wanted to feel that I was
OL,16,Fpart of something" following the
OL,17,Fsinger's death aged 31.
OL,19,F"I'm so heartbroken for that little
OL,20,Flad that I knew," she said.
