OL,3,CRebecca Ferguson 'tried reaching out'
OL,4,Cto X Factor co-star Liam Payne
OL,6,FDiscussing her time with Payne on The
OL,7,FX Factor, she continued: "When we all
OL,8,Flived together, and we toured
OL,9,Ftogether, we were like a family.
OL,11,F"So I just keep picturing that young
OL,12,Fboy, I just keep picturing how happy
OL,13,Fhe was.
OL,15,F"I'm still in a bit of shock."
OL,17,FFerguson said she found it
OL,18,F"disgusting" that there were pictures
OL,19,Fcirculating online, allegedly from
OL,20,FPayne's hotel room.
