OL,3,CRebecca Ferguson 'tried reaching out'
OL,4,Cto X Factor co-star Liam Payne
OL,6,FBut the singer said that it was "so
OL,7,Flovely that he was so loved".
OL,9,FIt comes after Ferguson posted a
OL,10,Fstatement on X, describing Payne as
OL,11,F"young, innocent and unaffected by
OL,12,Ffame" when they met at London Euston
OL,13,Ftrain station and shared a taxi
OL,14,Ftogether to the X Factor studio.
OL,16,FRepresentatives for Payne have been
OL,17,Fcontacted for comment.
